entry.name: Series Object Name
entry.definition: Name of the Database Series Object.

entry.name: Initiation Type
entry.definition: Acquisition initiation type. The Defined Terms are: 0 = started on count rate 1 = started after time delay 2 = started manually

entry.name: Number Energy Sets
entry.definition: Number of energy sets in this Series.

entry.name: Number MG Time Slots
entry.definition: Number of R-R Interval time bins.

entry.name: Number View Sets
entry.definition: Number of view sets in this Series.

entry.name: Series Comments
entry.definition: User-defined additional information about the series.

entry.name: Distance Prescribed
entry.definition: User prescribed whole body scanning distance.

entry.name: Series Type
entry.definition: Defines type of series. The Defined Terms are: 0 = static 1 = whole body 3 = multi-gated 6 = dynamic 9 = tomographic
